title: Who Will Pay the Price for Big Tech's Hubris?
description: WIRED’s editor in chief mulls what lies in store for Elon Musk and Sam Bankman-Fried, plus more thoughts on the past week’s headlines.

title: Twitter’s SMS Two-Factor Authentication Is Melting Down
description: Problems with the important security feature may be some of the first signs that Elon Musk’s social network is fraying at the edges.
